'''Charles Baudelaire''' neɣ Carl Budler, d yiwen n umedyaz amuqran n tmurt n Fransa.

Illul di Pari deg usegwas n 1821. Yemmut daɣen di Pari deg usegwas n 1867.

Adlis-is yettwasnen aṭas macci cwit d "Fleurs du mal" neɣ "Tigeǧǧigen n diri", id yessufaɣ deg usegwas n 1857.

== Isefra-s yettewasenen == 

